{"type": "article", "id": 20836, "title": "漏勺式的洗菜工具", "description": "", "date": "2016-01-18T07:35:07Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 53, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702112942OquQH5vT1YAMRDyc.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是专门用来洗菜的厨房工具，它也可以用来过滤。它由两个带漏孔的半圆组成，通过转动实现开合。它的把手也是一个管道，让自来水顺着上面流下去，然后快速转动来清洗，沥干后就直接倒入盘中。意大利的设计师 Viviana Degrandi 设计了它，获得了 2015 年的红点奖。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150630EHFj3qNTL2gchmez.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"799\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.76095238\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150631aTPc6iu5qnJjXv9d.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"248\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.23619048\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150631WyiDBn28FghwYaxu.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"770\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.73333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}